ğŸ“Œ What is Postman?
Postman is an API testing tool that allows developers to send requests, test responses, and debug APIs without writing code. It provides a user-friendly interface to interact with REST APIs.

ğŸ”¹ Why Use Postman?
âœ… Easily test APIs â€“ No need to write scripts.
âœ… Send different types of requests â€“ GET, POST, PUT, DELETE, etc.
âœ… Use authentication methods â€“ JWT, OAuth, API keys, etc.
âœ… Save and organize API requests â€“ Helps in project management.
âœ… View API responses â€“ Check status codes, headers, and response data.

